# sloom

UNDER DEVELOPMENT v 0.2.0

Sloom is a webscrapper / crawling library

## Setup

to get use 
```
pip install sloom
```

to update use
```
 pip install sloom --upgrade
 ```

 ## Documentation

 Simple program to run sloom:

 ```python
 import sloom

 sloom.run("https://example.com")

 ```
